[49m[38;5;10m+    170[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    171[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    172[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    173[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent with cross-institutional information-flow scope, longitudinal-store initialization with consolidated-care-plan model, multi-source data consolidation with reconciliation, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading with consolidated view, conversation handling with care-plan-grounded responses and gap-detection-aware reasoning, output safety screening with scope verification, action routing to humans with structured handoff, and care-management-team reporting with audit logging. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-source data consolidation pipeline, continuous gap-detection pipeline, action-routing with named human ownership, cross-institutional information-flow governance, and human-care-management-team workflow integration).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    174[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    175[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    176[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
